{"tid":1664440,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"試著說: Five demands, not one FEWER","createTime":"2019-10-20T06:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T15:40:10.000Z","uid":255362,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3b34809e63ed29a676dd0a3fa5b692bfab215e","tid":1664440,"uid":255362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2017/08/game-of-thrones-stannis-less.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Foyster.ignimgs.com%2Fwordpress%2Fstg.ign.com%2F2017%2F08%2Fgame-of-thrones-stannis-less.gif&h=92d9f6c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2017/08/game-of-thrones-stannis-fewer.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Foyster.ignimgs.com%2Fwordpress%2Fstg.ign.com%2F2017%2F08%2Fgame-of-thrones-stannis-fewer.gif&h=6bea5099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然感覺上可能 fewer 比 less 要難嗌，但係始終文法上比較正確。 Countable nouns 應該用 fewer, uncountable nouns 先至用 less.<br />\n<br />\n(同埋 &quot;fewer&quot; 同 &quot;F&uuml;hrer&quot; （即納粹德國的元首）讀法類近，亦可以講 &quot;Five demands, not one F&uuml;hrer&quot; 去映射 777 嘅極權統治。)"},{"pid":"3a1463d88c2096c880de4e2a012cd1f5a3349af7","tid":1664440,"uid":149611,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"唔好搞到禁複雜 拉"},{"pid":"483abe9cd40bd0292ee663491f5075de5affae4d","tid":1664440,"uid":56462,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a1463d88c2096c880de4e2a012cd1f5a3349af7","tid":1664440,"uid":149611,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"唔好搞到禁複雜 拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:16:24.000Z","msg":"咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b79af2f082c75197984b036034708b6fa6cd208","tid":1664440,"uid":308414,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:16:55.000Z","msg":"唔好改啦"},{"pid":"eca921337999022bbca1f02e13285487129ab1ad","tid":1664440,"uid":165772,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:19:26.000Z","msg":"不如巴打學好啲英文先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a9072184d688291e5508ca7b41d80d2b2bc760","tid":1664440,"uid":58570,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb3b34809e63ed29a676dd0a3fa5b692bfab215e","tid":1664440,"uid":255362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2017/08/game-of-thrones-stannis-less.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Foyster.ignimgs.com%2Fwordpress%2Fstg.ign.com%2F2017%2F08%2Fgame-of-thrones-stannis-less.gif&h=92d9f6c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2017/08/game-of-thrones-stannis-fewer.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Foyster.ignimgs.com%2Fwordpress%2Fstg.ign.com%2F2017%2F08%2Fgame-of-thrones-stannis-fewer.gif&h=6bea5099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然感覺上可能 fewer 比 less 要難嗌，但係始終文法上比較正確。 Countable nouns 應該用 fewer, uncountable nouns 先至用 less.<br />\n<br />\n(同埋 &quot;fewer&quot; 同 &quot;F&uuml;hrer&quot; （即納粹德國的元首）讀法類近，亦可以講 &quot;Five demands, not one F&uuml;hrer&quot; 去映射 777 嘅極權統治。)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"唔建議<br />\nFive demands not one less已廣為人知，要改反而令大眾有d知 有d唔知，叫得唔齊又弱咗聲勢，重蹈10點轉9點叫，最後冇人叫嘅覆轍"},{"pid":"731e72770ae82bc31b5badd4fa42deb9d7defc1f","tid":1664440,"uid":255362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40a9072184d688291e5508ca7b41d80d2b2bc760","tid":1664440,"uid":58570,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb3b34809e63ed29a676dd0a3fa5b692bfab215e","tid":1664440,"uid":255362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2017/08/game-of-thrones-stannis-less.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Foyster.ignimgs.com%2Fwordpress%2Fstg.ign.com%2F2017%2F08%2Fgame-of-thrones-stannis-less.gif&h=92d9f6c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2017/08/game-of-thrones-stannis-fewer.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Foyster.ignimgs.com%2Fwordpress%2Fstg.ign.com%2F2017%2F08%2Fgame-of-thrones-stannis-fewer.gif&h=6bea5099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然感覺上可能 fewer 比 less 要難嗌，但係始終文法上比較正確。 Countable nouns 應該用 fewer, uncountable nouns 先至用 less.<br />\n<br />\n(同埋 &quot;fewer&quot; 同 &quot;F&uuml;hrer&quot; （即納粹德國的元首）讀法類近，亦可以講 &quot;Five demands, not one F&uuml;hrer&quot; 去映射 777 嘅極權統治。)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"唔建議<br />\nFive demands not one less已廣為人知，要改反而令大眾有d知 有d唔知，叫得唔齊又弱咗聲勢，重蹈10點轉9點叫，最後冇人叫嘅覆轍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:23:37.000Z","msg":"我都有呢個疑慮。但係如果嗌英文口號上左國際文宣但係錯文法嘅話，好似唔好睇姐。<br />\n例如 <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2019/oct/16/hong-kong-protests-carrie-lam-to-deliver-key-annual-speech-as-legislative-council-resumes-live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Flive%2F2019%2Foct%2F16%2Fhong-kong-protests-carrie-lam-to-deliver-key-annual-speech-as-legislative-council-resumes-live&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=65617110\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2019/oct/16/hong-kong-protests-carrie-lam-to-deliver-key-annual-speech-as-legislative-council-resumes-live</a>"},{"pid":"a865615e1251b230f49f8d482a6313670b8882cc","tid":1664440,"uid":211848,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:27:40.000Z","msg":"唔建議改， 拉"},{"pid":"715019df0e56c78c948c29d26f3c91252eff7dca","tid":1664440,"uid":190322,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"Grammar freak"},{"pid":"54f73569617a72f300cac25de26fd1948a25c26d","tid":1664440,"uid":233651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:28:20.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"2bbd7d9d3b6067fede71abfa01a658be449dc8d6","tid":1664440,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:28:23.000Z","msg":"Fewer 一定要跟countable noun, 但係less可以當adverb用<br />\n如果講「Five demands, not one fewer.」Fewer就一定係指五大訴求 個感覺就好似係同緊同路人講我地唔好減少訴求咁<br />\n<br />\n而「Five demands, not one less.」Less 可以係adverb, 可以係叫政府回應, &quot;Do not respond one less&quot; 咁"},{"pid":"0b8ef6d24c960f37637e0505906a14a7a92e5ad6","tid":1664440,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Fewer 一定要跟countable noun, 但係less可以當adverb用<br />\n如果講「Five demands, not one fewer.」Fewer就一定係指五大訴求 個感覺就好似係同緊同路人講我地唔好減少訴求咁<br />\n<br />\n而「Five demands, not one less.」Less 可以係adverb, 可以係叫政府回應, &quot;Do not respond less&quot; 咁</blockquote>"},{"pid":"91c5894e52dd36c9921fe4028ef2f934a7b4da59","tid":1664440,"uid":255362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"715019df0e56c78c948c29d26f3c91252eff7dca","tid":1664440,"uid":190322,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"Grammar freak"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N4vf8N6GpdM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DN4vf8N6GpdM&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=07b7d800\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N4vf8N6GpdM</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682627a52b9547508f81ee6cc82e77e4f59b1734","tid":1664440,"uid":38915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0ac1333201898259ad1bc05c8229a2b0f9a343","tid":1664440,"uid":38915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點漏"},{"pid":"ff364cdbc1fe204e2cdc2e9524c39671bcb070eb","tid":1664440,"uid":150610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"d274ad440e92a559bb78c14a71eedd853e07cf95","tid":1664440,"uid":190277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:52:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dictionary.com/e/fewer-vs-less/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dictionary.com%2Fe%2Ffewer-vs-less%2F&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=8f155167\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dictionary.com/e/fewer-vs-less/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然 fewer 係 grammatically correct ，<br />\n但係用 less 嚟取代 fewer 都好多人係咁用。"},{"pid":"a84b858f630f57cf9906520b5fcf671560ab07e2","tid":1664440,"uid":53666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"From Wiki:<br />\n<br />\nUsage notes<br />\nSome[*] regard the use of the determiner less with countable quantities to be incorrect, stating that less should indicate only a reduction in uncountable quantity, or in size or significance, leaving fewer to indicate a smaller numerical quantity. For example, we should say less sugar, but fewer people, not *less people. Such a rule also allows distinctions such as:<br />\n<br />\nTheir troubles are fewer than ours, meaning &quot;Their troubles are not so numerous as ours.&quot;<br />\nTheir troubles are less than ours, meaning &quot;Their troubles are not so great as ours.&quot;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Nevertheless, less has been widely understood and commonly used as a synonym for fewer since it first appeared in Old English as l&aelig;s.</span></span>"}]}